1
00:00:00,001 --> 00:00:01,147
Back up!

2
00:00:04,233 --> 00:00:05,692
What happened out there?

3
00:00:07,567 --> 00:00:09,064
Do you know if somethin' happened?

4
00:00:09,066 --> 00:00:10,565
Does she look familiar?

5
00:00:10,567 --> 00:00:13,398
- This is my baby girl?
- What do you think?

6
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,064
Were you aware that one of the officers

7
00:00:15,066 --> 00:00:17,161
who processed the
Woodard scene went missing

8
00:00:17,164 --> 00:00:19,023
during the second investigation?

9
00:00:19,025 --> 00:00:20,872
There's no fucking way that backpack

10
00:00:20,875 --> 00:00:23,148
was in that crawlspace
when that mortar went off.

11
00:00:23,150 --> 00:00:24,926
Tells some story of how she's a princess

12
00:00:24,929 --> 00:00:27,523
from the pink rooms. Said
she, uh, lost a brother.

13
00:00:27,525 --> 00:00:29,016
They're looking for me.

14
00:00:29,018 --> 00:00:33,476
Tell him to leave me alone.
The man acting like my father!

15
00:00:33,479 --> 00:00:35,106
Children should laugh.

16
00:00:35,108 --> 00:00:37,007
There wasn't a lot of
laughter around here.

17
00:00:37,010 --> 00:00:38,523
I know Lucy wrote it

18
00:00:38,525 --> 00:00:40,189
when that director
showed me some pictures.

19
00:00:40,191 --> 00:00:42,831
Dan O'Brien's body was
found in a drained quarry.

20
00:00:43,650 --> 00:00:45,609
How you gonna talk to these people?

21
00:00:46,734 --> 00:00:48,000
We done what we done.

22
00:00:48,003 --> 00:00:50,823
I remember what we done,
I remember not to say.

23
00:00:50,826 --> 00:00:52,160
You walked away.

24
00:00:53,885 --> 00:00:54,946
Not this time.

25
00:02:19,577 --> 00:02:24,132
