00:52:42,634 --> 00:52:44,509
That she was.

771
00:52:48,300 --> 00:52:49,675
Yeah.

772
00:52:52,425 --> 00:52:54,966
It's 2015, isn't it?

773
00:52:56,300 --> 00:52:58,300
That's right, pal.

774
00:53:00,841 --> 00:53:02,893
"A lost child is a void

775
00:53:02,896 --> 00:53:06,423
that echoes backwards
and forwards in time.

776
00:53:06,425 --> 00:53:09,839
It encompasses not just the
rooms you were in with them

777
00:53:09,841 --> 00:53:12,215
and are no longer,

778
00:53:12,217 --> 00:53:16,089
or even those rooms you
will never enter together.

779
00:53:16,091 --> 00:53:18,881
The negation is deeper.

780
00:53:18,883 --> 00:53:23,964
It is the knowledge that in every room
you enter for the rest of your life,

781
00:53:23,966 --> 00:53:27,507
they should be there, and are not.

782
00:53:27,509 --> 00:53:31,217
And your memories of them
become totems to that absence.

783
00:53:32,965 --> 00:53:35,005
A lost child...

784
00:53:35,008 --> 00:53:38,800
is a story that's never allowed to end."

785
00:53:43,717 --> 00:53:46,143
Mrs. Hays will answer a few questions,

786
00:53:46,146 --> 00:53:49,298
and afterward she'll be
signing copies right here.

787
00:53:49,300 --> 00:53:51,089
Thank you.

788
00:53:51,091 --> 00:53:53,167
Ah, are there any questions?

789
00:53:53,170 --> 00:53:56,089
They sayin'...

790
00:53:56,091 --> 00:53:58,923
the girl alive now?

791
00:53:58,925 --> 00:54:01,698
There were fingerprints
found recently, yes.

792
00:54:01,701 --> 00:54:05,636
I'm writing about the
new investigation now.

793
00:54:06,731 --> 00:54:10,498
You got any idea where she is?

794
00:54:12,731 --> 00:54:14,107
Do they?

795
00:54:16,050 --> 00:54:19,008
Uh, no. Nobody does.

796
00:54:21,008 --> 00:54:23,717
- Are you...
- And what about your book?

797
00:54:25,383 --> 00:54:27,131
You got any theory here?

798
00:54:27,133 --> 00:54:31,381
You got some idea 'bout where she's at?

799
00:54:31,383 --> 00:54:33,076
Well, this...

800
00:54:34,258 --> 00:54:37,215
I wrote it when she was believed dead.

801
00:54:37,217 --> 00:54:39,089
So you don't know nothin'.

802
00:54:39,091 --> 00:54:41,798
You just...

803
00:54:41,800 --> 00:54:43,685
you just makin' your money...

804
00:54:43,688 --> 00:54:45,185
and milkin' they pain.

805
00:54:45,188 --> 00:54:46,875
Sir, the author has never claimed...

806
00:54:46,878 --> 00:54:48,378
Shame on you, woman!

807
00:55:03,342 --> 00:55:04,883
Dolls.

808
00:57:40,592 --> 00:57:42,091
The hell?

809
00:57:44,300 --> 00:57:45,717
Julie?

